	   <tr><td colspan=2>Recently been playing my alts alot, and when playing my chanty solo i've been wondering about the charm spells.<br><br>Here is my question... how often will Enchanter charm last on average with a CHA aroudn 115? I just got the spell last level and getting ready to really play with it my first time this morning (i work nights so play in mornings, great if you like soloing or small groups, horrible if your in spots that are BYOG).<br><br>Is it going to be something fairly reliable? (the mob stays my pet long enuogh to tank 1 or 2 other mobs for me, etc)<br><br>Since main is a druid, where charisma is something i never even play with (maybe at 85 right now, 90 tops), i've always been used to charm being nothing but a way to mez animals for a bit in a pinch. Never lasted that long for me, plus it's a sub par spell do the chanty charm line nayway.<br><br>Stats aren't a problem. I'm a Human Enchanter, buyt nicely twinked already. Int in hte 160's and the Cha around 115 as i said before.<br><br>Hoping for an answer, if theirs anything else info wise to answer the question let me know. Thanks in advance.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
