	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi i am new to this game i am lv 20 now but still learning alot. What is research and how do i research things to get my spells. I have asked other people in game but no one seems to want to answe me on this. Please help me.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
