	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey guys, I just wanted to remind everyone why an Enchanter is a must own class to have on your list. Particulary the newer enchanters or the newbies wondering if they should or should not make an enchanter.<br><br>1) You are one of the most desired class in the game. Casters want you for clarity. Melees want you for haste. Everyone wants you for crowd control.<br><br>2) Considered one of the easiest class to level. Every strong group needs you to be complete. No chanty = Weak group. You will get more group invites then any other class. Groups are usually saving a final spot on their group just for you.<br><br>3) You'll be rich once you get KEI. People are constantly shouting &quot;100pp for KEI plz.&quot; I've even seen in high level zones where people will pay 1kpp for KEI....many times also.<br><br>4) You'll get asked many times to help with high level raids because of your ability and as gratitude, the RL's usually will often give you priority over loots and assist you on your epic.<br><br>5) You and clerics will get spoiled rotten throughout your EQ life...unless you behave poorly.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
